| 0 := ‚ü®zero, one, one_zero_comm‚ü©
| (n+1) := ‚ü®(mk_hom_aux n).2.1,
    (succ n (mk_hom_aux n)).1, (succ n (mk_hom_aux n)).2‚ü©

/--
A constructor for chain maps between `‚Ñï`-indexed cochain complexes,
